    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80f1-9094-dc42b86b93ea",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors extracted logs from 133 students and extract general counts of activities and 5 indicators. The authors were able to predict the final grade with 65% accuracy and a recall of 54%. Predicting at the course’s halfway point, accuracy was actually 42%. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80f1-9094-dc42b86b93ea",
